OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FTo date, 43 festivals across the
OL,7,Fcountry have been called off this
OL,8,Fsummer. Factoring in last year too,
OL,9,Fthe total number which have cancelled
OL,10,Fentirely is more than 80.
OL,12,FThe Association of Independent
OL,13,FFestivals (AIF), an industry body
OL,14,Frepresenting more than 200 events,
OL,15,Fsays they fear that figure could
OL,16,Fexceed 100 by the end of the year.
OL,18,FLive music is more popular than ever,
OL,19,Fwith more than 37 million ticket sales
OL,20,Facross concerts last year according to
OL,21,Fthe UK Music Report for 2023.
