OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,F"It has become increasingly difficult
OL,7,Ffor independent festivals to operate
OL,8,Fin in the current climate. We know
OL,9,Fwe're not alone and many other
OL,10,Ffestivals are in a similar situation.
OL,12,FIt's a tough financial market out
OL,13,Fthere, it's tough so sell tickets
OL,14,Fbecause people haven't got the money
OL,15,Fand it's also tough to put events on
OL,16,Fbecause the cost of doing so is
OL,17,Fgetting so high".
