OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,F"As you come towards the event, you
OL,7,Fhire lots of companies, supply chain
OL,8,Fcompanies, and hundreds, if not
OL,9,Fthousands of freelancers.
OL,11,FThen of course you might have
OL,12,Fvolunteering opportunities too. So the
OL,13,Feffect every time a festival goes
OL,14,Fdown, the repercussions are huge.
OL,16,FLoads of jobs lost, loads of
OL,17,Fvolunteering opportunities are lost
OL,18,Fand future festival headliners do not
OL,19,Fget their first steps onto a stage." -
OL,20,FJohn Rostron, Association of
OL,21,FIndependent Festivals.
