OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,F"Last year, for example, we made quite
OL,7,Fa significant loss. So instead of
OL,8,Fbeing able to reinvest, we actually
OL,9,Fended up cutting stages, which means
OL,10,Fcutting creatives, cutting employment,
OL,11,Fcutting artists for the weekend, just
OL,12,Fto try and get our cost to a point
OL,13,Fwhere we can keep our ticket price
OL,14,Fdown, the ticket price is so sensitive.
