OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FA VAT cut, even for a year or two
OL,7,Fwould allow us to reinvest and keep
OL,8,Fbeing innovative. Festivals are a
OL,9,Fmassive part of our culture and
OL,10,Fheritage. It is something as a country
OL,11,Fwe do really well. So it would be such
OL,12,Fa shame to see our industry fade away".
